TextEng: No deals. I'm here for your death.
Text: 거래 안 해. 난 당신을 죽이러 왔어.

TextEng: Me not here for talk, but for death. Your death!
Text: 나 대화하러 온 거 아니야, 죽이러 왔어. 너 죽이러!

TextEng: Who are you?
Me not know who you is.
Why did you ambush me?
Why attacks me?
I intend to claim the bounty on you.
Me wants kill Wyvern for bounty!
Text: 나 와이번 죽이고 현상금 받고 싶어!

TextEng: Actually, I don't care to know who you are. Let us fight!
Text: 사실, 네가 누군지는 관심 없어. 싸우자!

TextEng: Me not care. Me just want fighting.
Text: 나 신경 안 써. 나 그냥 싸우고 싶어.

TextEng: Why were you originally imprisoned?
Why you gets in prison in first place?
Why should I listen to anything that you say?
Text: 왜 네가 하는 말을 들어야 하지?

TextEng: Me wonders why you think me need hears this.
Text: 나 왜 너 이 말 들어야 된다고 생각해?

TextEng: I want your ear, Wyvern.
Me just wants ear.
Enough talk, Wyvern. It's time for you to die.
Text: 말은 그만, 와이번. 이제 죽을 시간이야.

TextEng: Stop talking! Me kills you! Now!
Text: 말 그만해! 나 너 죽일 거야! 지금!

TextEng: How did you escape?
You don't wish to die and you want to make a deal?
You want live? Make deal?
That's nice, but I'm here for the bounty.
Text: 좋긴 한데, 난 현상금 받으러 온 거야.

TextEng: Me just wants bounty. Me not care about all this.
Text: 나 그냥 현상금 원해. 나 이거 신경 안 써.

TextEng: So be it. I agree.
Me likes deal. Me says sound good.
Text: 나 거래 좋아. 나 괜찮다고 생각해.

TextEng: Agreed, but only if you help me find the other escapees.
Text: 동의해, 단 다른 탈옥수들을 찾는 걸 도와준다면.

TextEng: Me does this if you lets me know where other criminal is.
Text: 나 이렇게 해줄게. 근데 너 다른 범죄자 어디 있는지 알려줘.

TextEng: No deal, you disgusting murderer! I'll kill you now!
Text: 거래 안 해, 역겨운 살인자! 지금 죽여주지!

TextEng: You sick murderer. Me kill now.
Text: 너 역겨운 살인자야. 나 지금 죽여.

TextEng: How you is escaping?
What do you propose?
You want make deal?
Go on.
What happened?
You were captured?
Your crimes sicken me! Die!
You bad bad man! Die!
You have kept your end of the bargain. Go into the wilderness and never return.
Text: 약속은 지켰어. 황야로 가고 절대 돌아오지 마.

TextEng: Okay now. You go now and no come back.
Text: 이제 됐어. 너 이제 가고 다시 오지 마.

TextEng: I think I've decided to kill you anyway.
Me not care. Me kill you anyway.
Text: 나 신경 안 써. 나 어쨌든 너 죽일 거야.
